constraint.name: Room Capacity
constraint.description: Number of seats must be >= enrolled students

constraint.name: Room Availability
constraint.description: A room cannot host more than one class at a time

constraint.name: Faculty Clash Avoidance
constraint.description: A teacher cannot teach multiple classes simultaneously

constraint.name: Student Group Clash Avoidance
constraint.description: A student/class cannot attend two lectures at the same time

constraint.name: Time Window Constraints
constraint.description: Lectures must fit within institution working hours (Mon-Fri, 8:00-18:00)

constraint.name: Course Load Fulfillment
constraint.description: Each course must be scheduled for its required lecture/tutorial/lab hours per week

constraint.name: Lab/Equipment Requirement
constraint.description: Courses requiring labs/projectors must be assigned only to suitable rooms

constraint.name: One Session, One Location
constraint.description: A session cannot be split across multiple rooms simultaneously

constraint.name: Faculty Availability
constraint.description: Lectures must not be scheduled when a teacher is unavailable

constraint.name: Exam Timetable Dependencies
constraint.description: Courses sharing students cannot have exams clashing

constraint.name: Legal/Ethical Constraints
constraint.description: No classes scheduled on national holidays, official breaks

constraint.name: Prerequisite Ordering
constraint.description: Some practicals must occur after theory lectures

constraint.name: Batch Splitting in Labs
constraint.description: If labs must be split into sub-batches, they must be assigned valid parallel slots/rooms

constraint.name: Curriculum Coverage
constraint.description: Every compulsory subject must appear in every semester's timetable

constraint.name: Section Uniqueness
constraint.description: Each section of a course must have a unique non-overlapping allocation

constraint.name: Class Hours Restriction
constraint.description: All classes must be scheduled between 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM (P3 to P8)

constraint.name: Mandatory Lunch Break
constraint.description: Each section must have at least one free period between 12:00-15:00 (P5-P7) every day

constraint.name: Minimize Gaps for Students
constraint.description: Avoid long idle times between lectures

constraint.name: Minimize Gaps for Teachers
constraint.description: Avoid unnecessary waiting between lectures

constraint.name: Balanced Daily Workload
constraint.description: Avoid overloading a class/teacher on a single day

constraint.name: Balanced Weekly Workload
constraint.description: Spread courses evenly across the week

constraint.name: Preferred Time Slots
constraint.description: Morning slots for core subjects, electives later

constraint.name: Avoid Early/Late Slots
constraint.description: Avoid 8 AM or 6 PM classes if possible

constraint.name: Avoid Consecutive Lectures
constraint.description: Reduce back-to-back lectures for both students and faculty

constraint.name: Teacher Preferences
constraint.description: Some teachers prefer specific days/times

constraint.name: Student Preferences
constraint.description: Certain electives preferred at non-conflicting times

constraint.name: Classroom Proximity
constraint.description: Assign classes/labs in physically close locations

constraint.name: Fair Resource Usage
constraint.description: Ensure equal distribution of premium rooms/labs among departments

constraint.name: Compact Schedules
constraint.description: Keep lectures grouped without large gaps

constraint.name: Avoid Overcrowded Days
constraint.description: Ensure no day has excessive lectures compared to others

constraint.name: Parallel Electives Handling
constraint.description: Electives chosen by different student groups should be scheduled without clashes

constraint.name: Faculty Load Balancing
constraint.description: Ensure workload distribution among teachers is fair

constraint.name: Guest Faculty Optimization
constraint.description: Group their classes into fewer days to minimize campus visits

constraint.name: Exam-Friendly Layout
constraint.description: Avoid overloading a day just before scheduled exams

constraint.name: Energy/Resource Optimization
constraint.description: Try to schedule in a way that minimizes unused rooms/electricity

constraint.name: Flexible Lunch Break
constraint.description: Allow lunch break in any one slot between 12:00-15:00 (P5, P6, or P7)

constraint.name: Pedagogical Constraints
constraint.description: Spread theory and labs logically (lab after related theory)

constraint.name: Seasonal/Contextual Adjustments
constraint.description: Summer classes in air-conditioned rooms, etc.

constraint.name: Equal Class Distribution
constraint.description: Classes should be distributed evenly across weekdays (2-4 classes per day per section)

constraint.name: Prevent Daily Overload
constraint.description: No section should have more than 4 classes in a single day

policy.name: Maximum Consecutive Classes
policy.description: No more than 3 consecutive classes for students

policy.name: Maximum Daily Load
policy.description: Maximum 6 classes per day for any section

policy.name: Faculty Daily Limit
policy.description: Maximum 8 teaching hours per day for faculty

policy.name: Lab Duration
policy.description: Lab sessions must be minimum 2 hours

policy.name: Room Change Time
policy.description: Minimum 10 minutes between classes in different buildings

policy.name: Preferred Morning Subjects
policy.description: Core CS subjects preferred in morning slots
